---- Modify Access to Remote Hosts -----------------

1. Choose Hosts from the Browse menu.

2. Select the host entry to modify from the
   Admintool:Hosts window.

3. Choose Modify from the Edit menu.

   The Modify window contains the selected host
   entry. 

4. Make the needed changes to the host name or the
   IP address.

5. Click on OK.

   The host information displayed in the main window
   is updated.
